{"word":"G3722 - ὄρθρος - órthros - or'-thros - Early in the morning","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὄρθρος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">órthros</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">or'-thros</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Early in the morning</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"அதிகாலை, காலை - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"daybreak, dawn"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the same as <a href=\"#/G3735 - ὄρος - óros - or'-os/3735\">G3735</a>; <i>dawn</i> (as <i>sun rise</i>, <i>rising</i> of light); by extension <i>morn:</i> - early in the morning.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1357/1357\">G1357</a>, <a href=\"#/G1882/1882\">G1882</a>, <a href=\"#/G3716/3716\">G3716</a>, <a href=\"#/G3717/3717\">G3717</a>, <a href=\"#/G3718/3718\">G3718</a>, <a href=\"#/G3719/3719\">G3719</a>, <a href=\"#/G3720/3720\">G3720</a>, <a href=\"#/G3721/3721\">G3721</a>, <a href=\"#/G3722/3722\">G3722</a>, <a href=\"#/G3723/3723\">G3723</a>"}]}